'''The Graveyard of the Dragons''' was the putative [[Planet/Legends|planet]] where all [[Duinuogwuin/Legends|Duinuogwuin]] traveled to die. The [[Graveyard of the Dragons]] of [[Xuaquarres]] was believed to be ''The'' Graveyard of the Dragons.

{{Planet-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
[[Jason Fry]], co-author of ''[[The Essential Atlas]]'', indicated in [[June]] [[2015]] that the Graveyard of the Dragons was excluded from [[Star Wars: The Essential Atlas Online Companion|''The Essential Atlas'' Online Companion]] because it was uncharted.<ref name="Email">{{EmailCite|email=File:EAOC discussion.jpg|creator=Jason Fry|date=2015-06-30}}</ref>

